---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';

const title = "Get a Quote | Parking Lot Striping Springfield MO";
const description = "Request a fast quote for commercial parking lot striping, ADA compliance, or fire lane markings in Springfield MO and Greene County.";
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description}>
  <Header />
  <div class="pt-28 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark text-center mb-4">Get Your Free Quote</h1>
      <p class="text-center text-xl text-concrete mb-4">Professional commercial parking lot striping in Springfield and Greene County. Fast response for ADA compliance, fire lanes, warehouse lines, and restriping.</p>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-dark">Request a quote via the form below or email us.</p>
        <p class="text-concrete mt-1">Email: <a href="mailto:quotes@springfieldlotstriping.com" class="text-brand-yellow hover:underline">quotes@springfieldlotstriping.com</a></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-concrete mt-2">Same-week availability for most commercial projects • Greene County focused</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-surface p-10 rounded-3xl mb-12">
        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mvzjkvpr" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Formspree configuration -->
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New Quote Request - Springfield Lot Striping">
          <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display:none">

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">Name</label>
              <input type="text" name="name" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-yellow" placeholder="Your full name" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">Business / Property Name</label>
              <input type="text" name="business" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-yellow" placeholder="Company or property name" required>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">Phone Number</label>
              <input type="tel" name="phone" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-yellow" placeholder="Best callback number" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">Service Needed</label>
              <select name="service" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-yellow">
                <option>Restriping</option>
                <option>ADA Compliance Striping</option>
                <option>Fire Lane Marking</option>
                <option>Warehouse / Industrial Lines</option>
                <option>New Layout or Full Design</option>
                <option>Not Sure / Assessment Needed</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">Lot Details &amp; Timeline</label>
            <textarea name="message" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-yellow h-32" placeholder="Approximate number of spaces, lot location (e.g. East Sunshine, James River corridor), deadline, or special requirements (ADA, overnight work, etc.)..." required></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full btn-primary py-4 text-lg shadow-md">Send My Free Quote Request →</button>
          <p class="text-xs text-center text-concrete">Fast response within 2 business hours. Same-week availability for most commercial projects.</p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-concrete">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-dark">Why Springfield Businesses Call Us First</h2>
        <p>We specialize exclusively in commercial parking lot striping and compliance work across Springfield and Greene County. No residential driveways. We understand the pressures facility managers and property owners face: tenant turnover, code inspections, delivery traffic, and the need for documentation that stands up to insurance and city reviews.</p>

        <h3>Fast, Documented, Commercial-Only</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Same-week or next-day scheduling for most jobs</li>
          <li>Early morning, overnight, or weekend work to minimize disruption</li>
          <li>Full photo and measurement documentation delivered after every project</li>
          <li>Experience with strip malls, warehouses, medical offices, apartments, retail, and industrial sites on East Sunshine, Glenstone, Campbell, and the James River corridor</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>What to Expect</h3>
        <p>When you contact us, we ask the right questions up front: stall count, current condition, any upcoming paving or sealcoating, ADA requirements, fire lane compliance needs, and tenant schedules. This lets us provide an accurate quote quickly and arrive prepared.</p>

        <p>Most standard restriping jobs on lots with 50–150 spaces are completed in a few hours. Larger or more complex projects (full ADA resets, warehouse 5S layouts, or new construction layouts) are quoted after a quick site review.</p>

        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <h3>How much does parking lot striping cost in Springfield?</h3>
        <p>Typical commercial restriping falls in the $850–$2,800 range depending on the number of stalls, condition of the asphalt, and whether any layout changes or ADA updates are required. We provide detailed quotes after reviewing your specific lot.</p>

        <h3>Do you handle ADA compliance work?</h3>
        <p>Yes. We regularly update accessible stalls, access aisles, van spaces, and signage to meet current Missouri and federal requirements. We can provide documentation suitable for inspections or property management records.</p>

        <h3>Can you work around my tenants and operating hours?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely. We specialize in low-disruption scheduling including overnight and early morning work for retail, medical, and warehouse properties.</p>

        <h3>Do you serve areas outside Springfield?</h3>
        <p>Yes — Nixa, Ozark, Republic, Battlefield, Rogersville, and the rest of Greene County. No travel fees for most jobs in our primary service area.</p>
        
        <h3>Can you provide documentation for inspections?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely. Every job includes a full documentation package with photos, measurements, and compliance notes suitable for city, insurance, or property management records.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Proven Process for Commercial Projects in Springfield</h2>
        <p><strong>1. Quote &amp; Assessment:</strong> We ask the right questions upfront (stall count, current condition, paving history, ADA/fire/warehouse needs, tenant schedules) and provide a transparent quote. On-site visits are scheduled quickly for complex jobs.</p>
        <p><strong>2. Preparation:</strong> Power washing, crack repair, and surface prep ensure maximum adhesion in Missouri's climate.</p>
        <p><strong>3. Precision Application:</strong> Professional equipment and high-visibility traffic paint deliver crisp, code-compliant lines with minimal disruption — often overnight or early morning.</p>
        <p><strong>4. Documentation &amp; Handover:</strong> Before/after photos, measurements, compliance certificates, and maintenance notes delivered for your records.</p>
        
        <h2>Local Challenges We Solve in Greene County</h2>
        <p>Springfield-area lots face heavy truck traffic on corridors like the James River Freeway and East Sunshine, frequent repaving, and strict enforcement. We use paints and techniques suited to clay soils, freeze-thaw cycles, and high-traffic commercial use. Our experience includes strip malls, medical plazas, warehouses, apartments, churches, and retail centers across Springfield, Nixa, Ozark, Republic, and Battlefield.</p>
        
        <p class="mt-6">Ready to get your lot compliant and professional? Request your free quote today.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>